orb-kubectl (optional, downloaded on-demand from GitHub Releases)

  orb-kubectl is a modified build of kubectl from the Kubernetes project
  with an added --retry flag for `kubectl port-forward`. It is distributed
  as a separate GitHub Release asset (not bundled in the Orbit app) and is
  downloaded only if the user opts in via Settings → Tools.

